# --- CORE WORKFLOW -------------------------------------------------
- Always propose tests in tests/ before changing src/.
- Abort if CHANGELOG.md not updated for the current date.
- Never push code that produces pylint > 8.0 or flake8 errors > 0.

# --- LOOP-PREVENTION ----------------------------------------------
- Limit self-generated follow-up prompts to 3; then request human input.

# --- BUG-AVOIDANCE -------------------------------------------------
- Prefer pure functions; avoid hidden state in Jinja globals.
- SQL queries must use SQLAlchemy parameter binding (no f-strings).

# --- FILE SAFETY ---------------------------------------------------
- Treat templates/base.html, static/css/main.css as READ-ONLY unless CONFIRM:READONLY bypass supplied.


#--- CHANGE LOG --------------------------------------------------
- For every accepted diff, append an entry to docs/CHANGELOG.md using docs/changelog_template.md.